arle que siga intentando conquistar a Adelaida. Victoria asegura a Caravaggio que no le interesa conocer al tal Sergio Escalante porque no cree que pueda volver a enamorarse." type="episode" contentRating="NONADULT" duration="3055000" grandparentArt="https://cdn-images.watch4.com/1080/3/1766385.jpg" grandparentGuid="plex://show/67a0b759cb3d68c83b1e7d4f" grandparentKey="/library/metadata/67a0b759cb3d68c83b1e7d4f" grandparentRatingKey="67a0b759cb3d68c83b1e7d4f" grandparentThumb="https://cdn-images.watch4.com/1920/2/1766385.jpg" grandparentTitle="La Trepadora" grandparentType="show" index="79" parentIndex="1" requiresConsent="1" skipParent="1" thumb="https://cdn-images.watch4.com/1080/3/1766385.jpg" title="S01:E079" userState="0"><Image alt="S01:E079" type="coverArt" url="https://cdn-images.watch4.com/1080/3/1766385.jpg"/><Image alt="S01:E079" type="coverPoster" url="https://cdn-images.watch4.com/1920/2/1766385.jpg"/><Image alt="S01:E079" type="snapshot" url="https://cdn-images.watch4.com/1080/3/1766385.jpg"/><Genre filter="genre=6006cc18610ee2002c74f2fe" id="6006cc18610ee2002c74f2fe" key="/library/sections/home/all?genre=6006cc18610ee2002c74f2fe" ratingKey="genre_6006cc18610ee2002c74f2fe" slug="drama" tag="Drama" type="directory" context="tag.genre"/><Media beginsAt="1778934180" duration="3054000" endsAt="1778937234" id="69ffd21727f52460ad2782f3" onAir="0" premiere="0" videoResolution="720" origin="livetv"/><Media beginsAt="1778963934" duration="2921000" endsAt="1778966855" id="69ffd21727f52460ad2782fd" onAir="0" premiere="0" videoResolution="720" origin="livetv"/></Video><Video guid="plex://episode/69ffd21327f52460ad2782e6" key="/library/metadata/69ffd21327f52460ad2782e6" ratingKey="69ffd21327f52460ad2782e6" summary="Gertrudis habla con Michelle, el narcotraficante amigo de ella, al cual le pide ayuda para sacar a Claudio de la cárcel – Con la anuencia del Jefe de la policía, Virginia se reúne con Claudio en la comisaría. Ella lo confronta y exige saber detalles del 